headline: RTX Fintech Names Electronic Trading Specialist Minor Huffman as Chief Technology Officer
summary: RTX Fintech & Research ("RTX Fintech"), a leading US electronic interdealer trading platform for interest rate swaps, today announced the appointment of Minor Huffman as Chief Technology Officer. Huffman will oversee RTX's global technology strategy and lead new infrastructure developments to ensure security, speed and scalability as the platform continues to grow.
